# State Management & Configuration

## State Management

- **Library**: vuex


> Use the existing state management library. Do not introduce alternative state solutions.





## Rules

1. Use environment variables or config files for environment-specific values — never hardcode
2. Manage application state through vuex — do not introduce alternative state libraries
4. Keep configuration separate from business logic
